comments: Best Teacher I have had so far. Great feedback and gives a new meaning to positive psychology!
This course was taught by the professors with extentive knowledge in helping all that need help,

Professor Jackson was incredibly well involved, empathetic, and gave incredible feedback on every assignment and weekly progress report. I was extremely impressed and pleased with the way he conducted himself in this class as no other instructor thus far has been as involved and positively motivating as Taures Jackson was. What a great professor!

Professor Jackson had to be one of the best professor I have had at Axia. He gave great feedback, and the class discussions was always interesting. He was sometimes picky about writing and grammar, but I needed that help.
